    "This helps students feel more comfortable and encourages them to express themselves freely in their writing.Research shows that the use of digital technology in teaching writing skills can significantly improve students' performance and reduce their apprehension towards writing.",
    "Studies have also explored the effectiveness of AI-powered writing tools in promoting learning behavior and technology acceptance [7].",
